---
import FAQItem from './FAQItem.astro';
---
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="faq-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Questions</span>
      <h2>Common questions.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <FAQItem question="When does Christ Note launch?">
        Spring 2026, on iPhone first. Join the waitlist to be notified.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Is it free?">
        A free tier covers a few sermons per month. A premium tier unlocks unlimited recordings, deeper AI summaries, and unlimited library storage.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="What about my privacy?">
        Recordings are encrypted in transit and at rest. Audio is processed for transcription and immediately discarded — only the text remains. We never share data.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Can I record without permission?">
        Christ Note is for personal use. Always check with your parish before recording publicly.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Is this only for Catholics?">
        It's built for Catholic Mass first — scripture references default to USCCB lectionary readings — but anyone can use it for any sermon, talk, or lecture.
      </FAQItem>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.faq {
  padding: var(--section-y) 0;
}
.faq-head {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--s-12);
}
.faq-head .eyebrow {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
}
.faq-head h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--fs-display-3);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.faq-list {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
</style>
